queries.name: dipdup_contract
queries.query: query dipdup_contract ($name: String!) {dipdup_contract_by_pk(name: $name) {address code_hash created_at kind name typename updated_at}}

queries.name: dipdup_contract_metadata
queries.query: query dipdup_contract_metadata ($id: Int!) {dipdup_contract_metadata_by_pk(id: $id) {contract created_at id metadata network update_id updated_at}}

queries.name: dipdup_head
queries.query: query dipdup_head ($name: String!) {dipdup_head_by_pk(name: $name) {created_at hash level name timestamp updated_at}}

queries.name: dipdup_index
queries.query: query dipdup_index ($name: String!) {dipdup_index_by_pk(name: $name) {config_hash created_at level name status template template_values type updated_at}}

queries.name: dipdup_meta
queries.query: query dipdup_meta ($key: String!) {dipdup_meta_by_pk(key: $key) {created_at key updated_at value}}

queries.name: dipdup_model_update
queries.query: query dipdup_model_update ($id: Int!) {dipdup_model_update_by_pk(id: $id) {action created_at data id index level model_name model_pk updated_at}}

queries.name: dipdup_schema
queries.query: query dipdup_schema ($name: String!) {dipdup_schema_by_pk(name: $name) {created_at hash name reindex updated_at}}

queries.name: dipdup_token_metadata
queries.query: query dipdup_token_metadata ($id: Int!) {dipdup_token_metadata_by_pk(id: $id) {contract created_at id metadata network token_id update_id updated_at}}

queries.name: dex_asset
queries.query: query dex_asset ($id: Int!) {dex_asset_by_pk(id: $id) {asset_type decimals id name symbol updated_at_block_id}}

queries.name: dex_asset_pool_reserve
queries.query: query dex_asset_pool_reserve ($id: Int!) {dex_asset_pool_reserve_by_pk(id: $id) {asset_id id pool_id reserve}}

queries.name: dex_pair
queries.query: query dex_pair ($id: String!) {dex_pair_by_pk(id: $id) {asset_0_id asset_1_id created_at_block_id created_at_txn_id dex_key fee_bps id pool_id}}

queries.name: dex_pool
queries.query: query dex_pool ($id: Int!) {dex_pool_by_pk(id: $id) {account dex_key dex_pool_id id lp_token_id}}

queries.name: dex_swap_event
queries.query: query dex_swap_event ($id: Int!) {dex_swap_event_by_pk(id: $id) {amount_0_in amount_0_out amount_1_in amount_1_out asset_0_reserve asset_1_reserve block_id event_index event_type id maker metadata name pair_id price tx_id tx_index}}

queries.name: dipdup_status
queries.query: query dipdup_status ($name: String!) {dipdup_status(where: {name: {_eq: $name}}) {type name level size updated_at}}
